allowClear.description: Whether to allow clearing after another click.
allowClear.description_zh: 是否允许在再次单击后清除。

defaultValue.description: The default selected date or date range.
defaultValue.description_zh: 默认选择的日期或日期范围。

max.description: Maximum value of a selectable range.

min.description: Minimum value of a selectable range.

nextMonthButton.description: Contents of the Next Month button on the navigation pane
nextMonthButton.description_zh: 导航窗格上的“下个月”按钮的内容

nextYearButton.description: Contents of the next Year button on the navigation pane
nextYearButton.description_zh: 导航窗格上的“下一年”按钮的内容

prevMonthButton.description: Contents of the Last Month button on the navigation pane
prevMonthButton.description_zh: 导航窗格上的“上个月”按钮的内容

prevYearButton.description: Contents of the Last year button on the navigation pane
prevYearButton.description_zh: 导航窗格上的“去年”按钮的内容

selectionMode.description: The selection mode. Disable selection when this prop is not set.
selectionMode.description_zh: 选择模式。未设置此道具时禁用选择。

shouldDisableDate.description: Set whether the date is disable selection. The min and max Settings are ignored
shouldDisableDate.description_zh: 设置日期是否禁用选择。最小和最大设置将被忽略

value.description: The selected date or date range.
value.type: Date | null when selection mode is "single". [Date, Date] | null when selection mode is "range"

events.name: onChange
events.description_zh: 在所选日期更改时触发。
events.params: (val: Date | null) => void when selection mode is "single". (val: [Date, Date] | null) => void when selection mode is "range".

events.name: onPageChange
events.description: Trigger when changed year or month.
events.description_zh: 更改年份或月份时触发。
